summary:
Simon has more than 17 years experience working with youth; on human rights issues, elections, HIV/AIDs, governance, peace building among others in Ghana, Sierra and Liberia.

Specialities: Programme development for youth, Training, Facilitation, Data Collection and analysis, Policy,  campaign planning and leading.
